<html>
  <head>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
      * {
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
      }
      .button {
        height:44px;
        width: calc(100% - 30px);
        max-width: 800px !important;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #cc0a2f;
        border-radius: 36px;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        position: relative;

        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-align: center;
      }
      a {
        width: calc(100% - 30px);
        max-width: 800px !important;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .button div {
        margin-top: 10px;
      }
      .text-button.primary{
        color: #cc0a2f;
      }
        .text-button.secondary {
          color: #00bae5;
        }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3><%= raw t('layouts.users.welcome') %></h3>
    <p>
      <%= raw t('.welcome_user', :user => @user.name.length > 0 ? @user.name : '') %>
    </p>
    <p>
      <%= raw t('.myteaco_link') %><br />
      <span style="font-weight: 500;"><%= @user.key %></span>
      <br />
      <br />
      <span style="font-weight: 500;"><% admin_url = show_administration_url(:user_key => @user.key) %></span>
      <a class="text-button primary" href="<%= admin_url %>">
        MyTeaCo Dashboard
      </a>
      <br />
    </p>
    <p>
      Solltest du die TeaCo-App f√ºr dein Smartphone installiert haben,
      kannst du dich mit deinem TeaCo-Account direkt in deiner App registrieren:
      <br />
      <br />
      <%
        teaco_fallback_app_url = api_register_in_app_url(:key => @user.key)
        teaco_direct_app_url = AppLinkGenerator.generate_registration_link(@user.key)
      %>
      <a href="<%= teaco_direct_app_url %>"
         href="<%= teaco_fallback_app_url %>"
         href="<%= teaco_direct_app_url %>">
        <div class="button">
          <div>
            Account in App Registrieren
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <br />
      <br />
      <span style="font-style: italic;">* Sollte dieser Button in deinem EMail-Client nicht funktionieren, nutze bitte den nachfolgenden Link: </span>
      <a class="text-button secondary" href="<%= teaco_fallback_app_url %>">Account in App registrieren</a>
    </p>
    <h4>
      <%= raw t('teaco_mailer.keep_link') %>
    </h4>
  </body>
</html>


